{"tid":1692732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能可以收TVB皮？","createTime":"2019-11-04T08:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:23:10.000Z","uid":142907,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6daf26258ec32a9a2b51f87e1c40d0f03289e1","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"家中藍絲父母日日睇TVB真係睇壞腦，轉去now佢都會轉返做TVB。廢中日日平平安安有電視睇就乜都唔理。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">令電視台癱瘓都係一樣不合作運動！</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能好似V煞套戲咁，用最普及嘅電視做媒介，直播一啲宣言，俾班廢中知道事實真相，而唔係比佢地睇完TVB就扮有關心時事，聚人皆醉我獨醒咁打飛機。起碼班手足做嘢嗰陣唔洗比人屈！<br />\n<br />\n或者用電台演說，鼓舞下士氣？（雖然電台已經冇乜人聽，但好多揸車嘅人都成日聽）正如好似希特拉嗰陣都係透過電台演講獲得大量支持者。（唔係想將納粹同香港扯上關係，不過民眾就係革命最大嘅力量）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有高手可以hack入TVB嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大氣電波</span></span></strong>頻道，救救港豬，令大家團結啲。我唔識大氣電波呢啲嘢，可能一切都諗得太理想，但真心希望可以討論下有冇可行性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好少出post，屌細力啲......</span>"},{"pid":"e46aed46cc19decf1cc0b812071ef015db070ff8","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"15488272c53fa21f9fa5d6a5aba0662f20969595","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n101"},{"pid":"ef1494dd0bb14a1d6a0e108b59ebb12dbacef48d","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n101"},{"pid":"14c699aa2b1a3d37f61c8bf16c622097b6ca1e66","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"4/10<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n101"},{"pid":"aa677a12d719c24ca8f16d26f1f13a7bb7984af5","tid":1692732,"uid":142907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:29:05.000Z",